://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-are-already-working-on-their-next-album-3498047">已经开始制作另一张新专辑来</a>取笑歌迷。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-rolling-stones-working-on-new-documentary-about-making-of-hackney-diamonds-3499529">滚石乐队正在制作有关“哈克尼钻石”制作的新纪录片的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
